text: Jean-Pierre Moris (7 June 1903 - 31 January 1985) was a Luxembourgian swimmer. He competed in the men's 100 metre backstroke event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1903 births Category:1985 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Luxembourg Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:People from Pétange Category:Male backstroke swimmers
